HTC Shares Rise in Taipei Trading On $18.5 Million Acquisition of Dashwire

-- B y   J a n e t   O n g
-- 
2011-08-08T01:06:37Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-08/htc-shares-rise-in-taipei-trading-on-18-5-million-acquisition-of-dashwire.html
HTC Corp. (2498)  gained in Taipei trading
after the smartphone maker agreed to buy 100 percent of Dashwire
Inc. for $18.5 million through its U.S. unit, according to a
statement to the Taiwan stock exchange on Aug. 5.  The stock rose 0.8 percent to NT$804 as of 9:05 a.m.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Janet Ong at 
 jong3@bloomberg.net  